{"tid":988341,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"今日發咗一個好奇怪嘅夢","createTime":"2019-01-20T03:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T08:27:15.000Z","uid":205742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eaa786ad610209845ad02e0d9934c13218866b80","tid":988341,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"我夢到係以前嘅中學，唔知點解要煮嘢食，我用咗一個好奇怪嘅煮嘢食嘅方法去整蛋糕，煮煮下唔知點解成個操場變到足球場嘅size，之後我孭住個好撚重嘅背囊，我甚至乎行唔到，要跪係度跣過去，但個操場好長，依啲人係到踢緊波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好辛苦咩住個袋先走到半場，然後就醒咗"},{"pid":"2551fafa1463f9dd82ada48ee797aec6e71a31d6","tid":988341,"uid":205742,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"係煮嘢食之前，我仲係到揼一個中學時候成日蝦我嘅人，係咁隔住個枕頭揼佢，佢好似還唔到手，但我覺得自己係留力，費事打死佢，連發夢都驚坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c24ee431e05826d8f66721e0634c4ec22160866","tid":988341,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:41:09.000Z","msg":"有勞巴絲解夢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6f9501dd35c162e11805007e55654c8c722bac","tid":988341,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:43:17.000Z","msg":"你係咪好有野心同上進心？<br />\n<br />\nps識解夢"},{"pid":"48ced2b79f5b308595bd6943fb87e1f6c2de51cb","tid":988341,"uid":129413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:43:18.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n<br />\n無人想知"},{"pid":"8fd4acac73a7021e3a06b783a080de71d66d71b3","tid":988341,"uid":205742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9e6f9501dd35c162e11805007e55654c8c722bac","tid":988341,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:43:17.000Z","msg":"你係咪好有野心同上進心？<br />\n<br />\nps識解夢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:45:15.000Z","msg":"正好相反，份人好頹"},{"pid":"177a012977a24238c7d94d4ab254792833ddad4e","tid":988341,"uid":190066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0